Without explicit CORS configuration, cross-origin behavior is unpredictable. Be explicit:

```js
const cors = require('cors');
app.use(cors({
  origin: process.env.ALLOWED_ORIGIN || 'http://localhost:3000',
  methods: ['GET'],
}));
```

---

